--- title: "Cotação do ouro - Parte 4 " subtitle: "Modelos lm-mars" author: "Pedro Lima" date: "2023-08-05" categories: [Modelos Estatísticos, Série-Temporal,R] toc: true toc-depth: 3 draft: true --- ::: {.cell} ::: ::: {.cell hash='index_cache/html/unnamed-chunk-2_a76af237a2ee277a9fa1f2bb8a0cf36e'} ::: ::: {.cell hash='index_cache/html/unnamed-chunk-3_da42cf6586779db4fc129bf9135930a1'} ::: ::: {.cell hash='index_cache/html/unnamed-chunk-4_68c026b0397be5b5a71b2622050402d3'} ::: ::: {.cell hash='index_cache/html/unnamed-chunk-5_7b6ea7d841062cd9687c466263828414'} ::: {.cell-output-display} ![](index_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-5-1.png){width=1440} ::: ::: ::: {.cell hash='index_cache/html/unnamed-chunk-6_1dc9cff096645084a55b09e2b96b9b42'} ::: {.cell-output-display} ![](index_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-6-1.png){width=1440} ::: ::: ## Modelos - Trend: Modeled using as.numeric(date) - Seasonal: Modeled using month(date) ::: {.cell hash='index_cache/html/unnamed-chunk-7_ce9925f704525cc57c270d90577a2060'} ```{.r .cell-code} lm_model <- model_fit_lm <- linear_reg() %>% set_engine("lm") %>% fit(media ~ as.numeric(mes) + factor(month(mes, label = TRUE), ordered = FALSE), data = training(splits)) ``` ::: ::: {.cell hash='index_cache/html/unnamed-chunk-8_19ff08ef845324b06e7112e1ada93bc0'} ```{.r .cell-code} mars_model <- # receita do modelo model_spec_mars <- mars(mode = "regression") %>% set_engine("earth") #receita para preparar os dados recipe_spec <- recipe(media ~ mes, data = training(splits)) %>% step_date(mes, features = "month", ordinal = FALSE) %>% step_mutate(date_num = as.numeric(mes)) %>% step_normalize(date_num) %>% step_rm(mes) #colocando as receitas em um fluxo de trabalho e ajustando o modelo wflw_fit_mars <- workflow() %>% add_recipe(recipe_spec) %>% add_model(model_spec_mars) %>% fit(training(splits)) ``` ::: ## Comparando os modelos ::: {.cell hash='index_cache/html/unnamed-chunk-9_1abf8e341f532f8154e6918e46eb2fe1'} ```{.r .cell-code} model_table <- modeltime_table( lm_model, wflw_fit_mars ) ``` ::: ## Calibrando ::: {.cell hash='index_cache/html/unnamed-chunk-10_e4466a2b9d88a5b3378ad0514a842e60'} ```{.r .cell-code} calib_table <- model_table %>% modeltime_calibrate(testing(splits)) ``` ::: ## Residual ::: {.cell hash='index_cache/html/unnamed-chunk-11_d6cd239def334f9154e0e2a8fbd32ef6'} ```{.r .cell-code} # calib_table %>% # modeltime_residuals() %>% # plot_modeltime_residuals( # .type = "seasonality", # .interactive = FALSE # ) ``` ::: ## Accuracy ::: {.cell hash='index_cache/html/unnamed-chunk-12_0fe6610341d8a405b483d45653c37475'} ```{.r .cell-code} calib_table %>% modeltime_accuracy() ``` ::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout} ``` # A tibble: 2 × 9 .model_id .model_desc .type mae mape mase smape rmse rsq 1 1 LM Test 10.5 5.89 2.30 6.09 11.5 0.624 2 2 EARTH Test 13.3 7.49 2.92 7.79 14.6 0.580 ``` ::: ::: ## Test set visualization ::: {.cell hash='index_cache/html/unnamed-chunk-13_887be7760d5b76560367e867666eb59e'} ```{.r .cell-code} calib_table %>% modeltime_forecast( new_data = testing(splits), actual_data = gold_mean ) %>% plot_modeltime_forecast() ``` ::: {.cell-output-display} ```{=html}
``` ::: ::: ## Validação Cruzada ::: {.cell hash='index_cache/html/unnamed-chunk-14_f7b3ea477cf1ebd3ca8804de08e6d0f0'} ```{.r .cell-code} resamples_fitted <- model_table %>% modeltime_fit_resamples( resamples = cv, control = control_resamples(verbose = FALSE) ) resamples_fitted ``` ::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout} ``` # Modeltime Table # A tibble: 2 × 4 .model_id .model .model_desc .resample_results 1 1 LM 2 2 EARTH ``` ::: ::: ::: {.cell hash='index_cache/html/unnamed-chunk-15_133004ff7d7ee9911f5d74dc8819fba8'} ```{.r .cell-code} resamples_fitted %>% plot_modeltime_resamples( .point_size = 3, .point_alpha = 0.8, .interactive = FALSE ) ``` ::: {.cell-output-display} ![](index_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-15-1.png){width=1440} ::: ::: ::: {.cell hash='index_cache/html/unnamed-chunk-16_eddbe8a9e29c8c983270d76cfe11162d'} ```{.r .cell-code} resamples_fitted %>% modeltime_resample_accuracy(summary_fns = mean) %>% table_modeltime_accuracy(.interactive = FALSE) ``` ::: {.cell-output-display} ```{=html}

``` ::: ::: ## Forecast future ::: {.cell hash='index_cache/html/unnamed-chunk-17_97ce0f5f9007e0a070aca6a238d6962c'} ```{.r .cell-code} future_forecast_tbl <- calib_table %>% modeltime_refit(gold_mean) %>% modeltime_forecast( h = "1 year", actual_data = gold_mean ) ``` ::: ::: {.cell hash='index_cache/html/unnamed-chunk-18_0478fd0f8e88022fdedd8cc57cb4f9d0'} ```{.r .cell-code} future_forecast_tbl %>% plot_modeltime_forecast() ``` ::: {.cell-output-display} ```{=html}
